TextEng: Could I ask you some questions?
Me want ask questions.
Goodbye.
Do you know anything about what causes it?
Have you heard anything about strange animals in the area?
Text: 그 구역에 있는 이상한 동물들에 대해 들은 것이 있나요?

TextEng: Is there anything going on in this area of the city?
Text: 이 구역에서 무슨 일이 일어나고 있는지 말해 주시겠어요?

TextEng: You know how you gets it?
You hear 'bout weird animals around here?
What go on 'round here?
Anything else you can tell me?
You knows something else maybe?
Maybe you've heard of something of interest?
I'd be interested in work, if you know of anything.
Maybe you hears something interesting?
Me want work.
Could you tell me anything about the plague?
Text: 역병에 대해 뭐라도 말해줄 수 있어?

TextEng: You know 'bout plague, maybe?
I want to ask you something else.
Me have other question.
I need some directions.
Neverwinter big place. Me need directions.
Why are you out here on the street? You're sick, you should be inside somewhere.
Text: 왜 거리에 나와 있어? 아픈데 어딘가 안으로 들어가야지.

TextEng: How has the plague affected your trade?
Text: 역병이 네 장사에 어떤 영향을 미쳤어?

TextEng: Why you out here on street? You sick, should be inside.
Text: 왜 거리 나와 있어? 너 아파, 안에 있어야지.

TextEng: Plague make your trade very bad, yeah?
Let me ask you something else, then.
Me have other question.
A gold or two? For you? You must be joking.
Golds? For you? You is joking, ha ha!
Err... about those sores...
You haves sores. You gots plague, no?
Text: 너 종기 있네. 역병 걸린 거지?

TextEng: Why wouldn't you go to the Moonstone Mask?
Text: 왜 월장석 가면 여관에 가지 않았나요?

TextEng: Why not Moonstone Mask?
Text: 왜 월장석 가면 여관 안 가?

TextEng: But you certainly don't need the coin if, ah...
Text: 근데 당신은 돈이 필요 없잖아, 그러니까...

TextEng: You not need coin if you going to, umm...
Text: 너 그럴 거면, 음... 돈 필요 없지?

TextEng: You have the plague?! Get away from me!!
You has plague?! Get away!!
Waste coin on you? I think not.
Text: 너한테 돈을 낭비해? 절대 안 돼.

TextEng: I have nothing to give.
Here... take a gold piece.
Take this: 100 gp. Go and find someplace warm tonight, and rest.
Text: 이걸 받아: 금화 100개. 가서 오늘 밤 따뜻한 곳을 찾아 쉬어.

TextEng: Waste coin? Me thinks not.
Me has nothing to give.
Here... you take gold piece.
Text: 여기... 너 금화 한 닢 받아.

TextEng: Take this: 100 gp. You go and finds someplace warm, and rest.
Text: 이거 받아: 금화 100개. 너 가서 따뜻한 곳 찾아서 쉬어.

TextEng: <StartAction>[Ignore her]</Start>
I could offer you mercy. A quick and painless death.
Text: 자비를 베풀 수는 있지. 빠르고 고통 없는 죽음을.

TextEng: Me can give mercy. Quick death, no pain.
Text: 나 자비 줄게. 빨리, 안 아프게 죽여 줄게.
